"BasalTop® is available in two sizes of length (297 and 440 cm) and three different thicknesses (ST, SM and SX).
From the point of view of fire risk, BasalTop® is classified:
• REI30' - in relation to fire resistance, pursuant to of the EN 13501-2:2009 standard;
• B-s2, d0 - related to reaction to fire, senses of the EN 13501-1:2009 standard;
• Broof(t3) - in relation to the external action of the fire, according to the test methods foreseen by the UNI CEN/TS 1187:2012.
"
